<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l10"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Morıcʒ vnd <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l11">ob man eẅch in <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> ſtett <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> auf <expan>heẅſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> mıt <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>hawff<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchıken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l12">wölt wıe Jr eẅch halten ſölt / Nu als Jr von vns gefertıgt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_264_line_1571387910068_296">ſeyt </ab></add> daʒ wır eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l13">den von <expan>Eg<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu hılff ır ſtat helffen ʒuretten vnd ʒubehalten / als <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l14">dıe huſſen geſandt haben vnd ob man eẅch <expan>yend<ex>er</ex>t</expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>ſwohin</expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l15"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> form wenden wölt daʒ Jr des nıht tun ſöltet / <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l16">
<add>ſıch</add> dıe huſſen ſo nahen . vor der ſtat ʒu Eger <expan>leg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd arbeyten wurden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l17">daʒ man mıt <expan>eıne<ex>m</ex></expan> eylen etwas guts <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe huſſen getrawet <expan>ʒuſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l18">da möchtet Jr auch ʒu <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> vnd darnach <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> in der ſtat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l19">ʒu <expan>beleıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> in dem form als vor . Alſo ıſt auch noch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> meynung </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l20">daʒ Jr dıe ſache / alſo handeln vnd halten ſüllet . So <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l21">in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>brıef<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vmb <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache auch <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r2l22"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>ub</ex>ſıgıllo</expan> <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>ıs</expan> tucher <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſ</ex>rıcıuiu<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>aſce<ex>n</ex>ſıo<ex>n</ex>ıs</expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nj</expan> </ab>
